enumerations.name: PncGatewayTypeEnum
enumerations.note: Defines the PncGateway roles. Aggregated by CommunicationConnector.pncGatewayType

literals.name: active
literals.description:
The active PncGateway functionality shall be performed

literals.name: none
literals.description:

literals.name: passive

Tags: atp.EnumerationLiteralIndex=2
